#!/usr/bin/env ssc-tools run --v1
---
name: scljet-write-check
description: Emit the bytes of SclJet's empty-database writer for byte-exact comparison
backends: [int]
---

# SclJet empty-database writer check

[ByteSlice, ByteError, byteSliceToList, emptyDatabase](std/scljet/index.ssc)

```scalascript
def emitBytes(pageSize: Int): Unit =
  emptyDatabase(pageSize) match
    case Right(bytes) => println(pageSize.toString + ":" + byteSliceToList(bytes).toString)
    case Left(error) => println(pageSize.toString + ":ERROR:" + error.message)

emitBytes(512)
emitBytes(1024)
emitBytes(4096)
emitBytes(65536)
```
